# Technologies

This document outlines the key technologies used in the Hub project.

## Frontend (Client)

- **Framework**: React 19
- **Build Tool**: Vite 6
- **Language**: TypeScript 5.7
- **Styling**: SASS
- **Testing**: Jest, React Testing Library
- **Navigation**: Norigin Spatial Navigation

## Backend (Server)

- **Runtime**: Node.js 22+
- **Framework**: Express.js
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: esbuild
- **Database**: Redis (via ioredis)

## Voice & Gaming Integration

- **Volley Platform SDK**: Voice gaming platform integration

## Development Tools

- **Linting**: ESLint 9+
- **Formatting**: Prettier
- **Versioning**: semantic-release
- **Commit Linting**: commitlint